Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘的移動要塞侵攻作戰被阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球得以保全
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A.G 151年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 笑起來多像你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 像亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字叫吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真忍心扔下這可愛的孩子去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後一次任務
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會有這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣善良的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不該上戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想讓他們生活在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有戰爭的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 現在必須戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時光飛逝…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是勇氣紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是漫長戰爭開始的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會見到父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天國的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屈身於紅色星球的戰士們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們理想鄉的實現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的計劃即將 進入最終篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄揚在地球神聖大地的日子不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要大家的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫蒂 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣場上的機動戰士展快要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到個絕佳的景點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去就上車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:04:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勒布魯斯 考出駕照了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這車是問爸爸借的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 有個派對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像是吉歐爺爺的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐最親爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 哪裏有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BIGRING防線內發現未知物體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綜合解析系統認為90%是維甘移動要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有發現這龐然大物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士部隊緊急出動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時命令周邊艦隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敵方移動要塞上 發現巨大熱量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是高功率光束武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了嗎 德勒爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始的鐘聲 響起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這感覺 是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 你父親的遺物？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛基沒聽說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐父親的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是聯邦軍機師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我出生後不久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一次調查漂流船的任務時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 別瞎說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後 軍隊前往調查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了這塊AGE裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 地球上也要打仗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人… 那就是維甘…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急召回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知不當班的士官 會還他們假期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告機動戰士隊情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭克斯小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯小隊也即將出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 什麼勇氣紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 這就出發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜路亞　喬納森
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪克　德比克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部不會把壞情況告訴前線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是聽見了吧 皮特的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮特… 那個通訊員？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次聽到皮特那種發顫的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他外遇被老婆發現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可見情況之危急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 戰場福爾摩斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這次不同往常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別大意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇·阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cnanche CUSTAM 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 情況不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會有事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名為伊澤爾坎特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活在火星圈的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨立國家維甘的代表者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 地球種
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘在此宣佈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式開始侵略地球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵略地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各軍區報告出現維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅限於奧利巴諾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多的維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直隱藏在地球上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民們請迅速前往
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿倫特河的避難區
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複 居民們請迅速前往阿倫特河…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停車 勒布魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏有孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再耽擱我們自身難保
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我在這裏下車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫蒂 你們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說我沒勸過你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.96,0:11:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著三個孩子打算這麼過來？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就去喊軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕 一起過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去避難區吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在這裏做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去避難區
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們被落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用您的車送他們走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民去阿倫特河避難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒接到通知嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍對平民孩子見死不救？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上士 事態緊急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快上來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫蒂 孩子拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事？ 不上車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也和吉歐一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你照顧好這些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺的高達是最強的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 上來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上車
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我們去哪兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啟動高達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 救世主登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天該告訴我藏高達的地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機翼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力拉操縱桿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛起來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是核心戰機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心戰機 那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候混進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧利巴諾茲被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓天神號做好出發準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管那麼多 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號是爺爺以前搭乘的戰艦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然是艘老舊船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要有那艘船和高達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧利巴諾茲就有救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達在那上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接駕駛核心戰機靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跳上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西的駕駛就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人駕駛不了它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Scepter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來會變形成高達是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是變形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是合體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合體？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:17:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達是由G-Scepter和核心戰機合體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組成一台機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上開始合體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是還在飛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 電腦會負責細節操作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…這也太突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 試試
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 把AGE裝置插入右手插口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後打開30號到35號開關
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據屏幕指示拉動拉桿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後按下操縱桿上的G鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就現在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達AGE-3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬆懈 好戲才剛開場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕嗎 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 驅動高達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且 繼承高達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來 驅動高達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了 可是怎麼做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達的操縱方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你玩的模擬戰一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是普通的遊戲機？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺為了這一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束軍刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放跑它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是用天神號光子爆破炮技術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研發的新武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西格瑪希斯步槍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲裏打過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它載有大量彈藥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果成功引爆…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又進化了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後你就是高達的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又與我過不去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它從上面來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.71,0:23:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰火籠罩的城市中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:24:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦船再次啟航
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.79,0:24:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反擊的閃光是否預示著未來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.85,0:24:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭城市
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.65,0:24:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.62,0:24:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘耗時多年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.48,0:24:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將刺客派往地球
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.41,0:24:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為一起掀起精心策劃的突襲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.58,0:24:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球從內部瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.87,0:24:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夜之間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.37,0:24:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再只屬於地球聯邦統治
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
